---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  pageTitle="Privacy Policy | MAUI Day"
  pageDescription="Privacy policy for MAUI Day."
>
  <section class="bg-white text-gray-600 text-md py-40">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-brand-dark text-4xl font-header font-bold mb-8">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-md text-base mb-8">
          This privacy policy explains how MAUI Day collects, uses, and protects your information.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-brand-dark text-2xl font-header font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Newsletter</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-md text-base mb-8">
          When you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your name and email address. We use this information to send you updates about MAUI Day. We do not share your data with third parties for marketing purposes. You can unsubscribe at any time via the link in our emails.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-md text-base mb-4">
          The subscribe form uses Google reCAPTCHA to prevent spam. View their privacy policy and terms of service at the links below.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-2 mb-8 text-gray-700 text-base leading-6">
          <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-extra hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-extra hover:underline">Google Terms of Service</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="text-brand-dark text-2xl font-header font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-md text-base mb-8">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact the organisers via the details on this site.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
